string.value: There seems to be something left for you to do. Talk to #b#p1013203##k at the #b#m922030000##k.

#p1013203# tells you to climb up to the #m922030020# once again while the guard is gone and enter the safe to eliminate the #r#o9300390##k inside. He says that you need to eliminate the monster quicky because it is very dangerous.\r\n\r\n#o9300390##r #a225841##k
You returned after eliminating the #o9300390#. #p1013203# says that you did a great job and that you played a big role in helping Maple World. But why do you feel so uneasy...?
I am going to give you one last mission. Thanks to all your great work, one of our members has unlocked the First Door of #m922030011#.
You must now go back up to #m922030020# and re-enter the Safe. Go in there and eliminate #r#o9300390##k, the monster.
#o9300390# is a scary, scary monster. You're going to have to eliminate him as fast as you can or we'll all be in danger. Please hurry.
What? What's the matter? Are you unhappy about something that I've discussed about our plans?

Thank you for getting rid of #o9300390#. You've done some great work. You must be tired now. Why don't you get some rest. Another member will take it from here.\r\n#L0##b#o9300390# said something strange.#l\n#k
Really? Well now, I wouldn't worry about it. #o9300390# may seem stupid, but it's actually really conniving and tries to confuse people. Don't think too much about it.
I will talk to you again when there's another mission for you.
You haven't eliminated #r#o9300390##k yet? Just go to the Safe on the top of #m922030020# and eliminate it. Go.
